</p></div>"}

Pull the left paracord across the above of the black paracord through the right loop formed just now. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/ca/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/ca/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet3.jpg/aid4336361-v4-728px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Pull the knot as tight as possible to make it compact and in shape. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c0/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/c0/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet4.jpg/aid4336361-v4-728px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-5Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

About the King Cobra , it is actually the same as the cobra's knot before. Pull the right paracord beneath the cobra paracord but above the left paracord. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/ed/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet1.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/e/ed/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet1.jpg/aid4336361-v4-728px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Pull the knot tight. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/56/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet2.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/5/56/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet2.jpg/aid4336361-v4-728px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Repeat. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c5/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/c5/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet3.jpg/aid4336361-v4-728px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Cut the extra cords and burn its end . {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/5e/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/5/5e/Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet4.jpg/aid4336361-v4-728px-Make-a-Paracord-550-Bracelet-Without-Buckle-%28Cobra-Stich-Followed-by-King-Cobra%29-Step-11Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
